{"tid":31472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英盜賊扮成假人模特兒 偷走價值5.6萬衣物","createTime":"2016-12-09T16:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T04:06:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48a388fe40edcd700e3d6e3f959dc2a45e4e7e9c","tid":31472,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:47:51.000Z","msg":"英國西薩塞克斯郡一家百貨公司近日遇上離奇盜竊案&mdash;&mdash;一批盜賊扮成假人模特兒，在店里一動不動等待一整天，待店門關上隨即大肆搜掠，偷走近1萬英鎊（約5萬6000令吉）的衣物。 <br />\n<br />\n百貨公司職員說，公司配備了一個複雜的警報系統，如果有人試圖闖入，立即會發現。 <br />\n<br />\n這些試圖行竊的盜賊事前曾扮作店內的假人，穿著與店內假人相同的衣服，一動不動，直至商店關閉再行事。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，盜賊在逃走時經過走火通道觸動警報，才導致暴露。 <br />\n<br />\n職員認為，這批盜賊是有策劃地犯罪，難以想像他們能一整天紋風不動。警方表示正調查案件，已經調取內部監控追查煩人。"},{"pid":"164906639f0d5a3d7566e1bfb020c5d5c13d7a6a","tid":31472,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T21:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf6a75b9a39dd3c0a5095b7aeea7937336ec120","tid":31472,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有恆心"},{"pid":"b9fcc614135211009e60b71d22b4606ff9b2f5ff","tid":31472,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:25:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9887e6edd3e59e315eb64d68648493fd7c72d222","tid":31472,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:30:11.000Z","msg":"好耐之前香港叫人小心財物個個廣告"},{"pid":"1b8470c45f54cad9e697c37d142dbfb8da530760","tid":31472,"uid":12647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:32:06.000Z","msg":"mannequin challenge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7d5daba1faf996cb71a08907d494847d218423","tid":31472,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"咩叫做「追查<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">煩人</span>」？"},{"pid":"5559f608